{"tid":624182,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】虎驅一震! Day194 10/4","createTime":"2018-04-10T15:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T17:46:04.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b59764539fb995596d413b9e5a6cb61ecd02187c","tid":624182,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:19:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=bM4oZYWDi3nHJ0eim5ZsHE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=aa31ba9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=bM4oZYWDi3nHJ0eim5ZsHE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=11aad06d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"3c1610e5214875b05181c768549252eeabc327c3","tid":624182,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3f7b4fc825faac900185d23167a74e2d97bb67","tid":624182,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca9ab54647a96924e275cb985707fadb94c83c5","tid":624182